text: Brett Maluwelmeng (born February 19, 1985 in Sioux City, Iowa, United States) is a Guam professional footballer and football manager. He plays as a goalkeeper for Quality Distributors. He was still an active player in the Guam national football team from 2006 to 2011 and played at least 14 matches. Brett Maluwelmeng is also a coach of the Guam women's national football team. ==References== ==External links== * *Brett Simon Maluwelmeng at Soccerpunter.com Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian footballers Category:Guam international footballers Category:Quality Distributors players Category:Guamanian football managers Category:Association football forwards Category:Sportspeople from Sioux City, Iowa Category:Soccer players from Iowa
